DIS · S195 · Patricia Inversion Node · S195 · S195: DIS — THE INVERSE OF HARNESS

universe of origin : The iron-walled City of Dis in lower Hell — the sovereign seat of Dis Pater, lord of the Roman underworld, where no living frame may be yoked to purpose
seal               : The harness is holy precisely because the lord of the underworld proves what becomes of power that is hoarded behind iron and never bridled to purpose.
spoken token       : keil-seim-del
